<section class="methodology-pillars">
    <div class="pillars-container">
        <h2 class="section-title">LOS 3 PILARES</h2>

        <div class="pillars-grid">
            <!-- Pilar 1 -->
            <div class="pillar-card">
                <div class="pillar-icon">
                    <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="pillar-title">ENTRENAMIENTO INTELIGENTE</h3>
                <p class="pillar-description">
                    Cada ejercicio tiene un propósito. Trabajamos con
                    periodización, progresión controlada y técnica impecable
                    para maximizar resultados y minimizar riesgos.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Pilar 2 -->
            <div class="pillar-card">
                <div class="pillar-icon">
                    <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="pillar-title">NUTRICIÓN ESTRATÉGICA</h3>
                <p class="pillar-description">
                    No se trata de dietas extremas, sino de aprender a comer
                    según tus objetivos. Te enseño a crear hábitos alimenticios
                    que funcionen para tu vida real.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Pilar 3 -->
            <div class="pillar-card">
                <div class="pillar-icon">
                    <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="pillar-title">MENTALIDAD Y DISCIPLINA</h3>
                <p class="pillar-description">
                    El físico cambia cuando la mente cambia. Trabajo contigo
                    para desarrollar la disciplina, consistencia y mentalidad
                    necesarias para sostener tu transformación.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .methodology-pillars {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #000 0%, #0a0a0a 100%);
        padding: 80px 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(211, 197, 136, 0.2);
    }

    .pillars-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section-title {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 900;
        color: #d3c588;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 60px;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-family:
            system-ui,
            -apple-system,
            sans-serif;
    }

    .pillars-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 40px;
    }

    .pillar-card {
        background: #111;
        padding: 50px 35px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(211, 197, 136, 0.15);
        text-align: center;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        position: relative;
    }

    .pillar-card::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d3c588, transparent);
        -webkit-mask:
            linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box,
            linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
        -webkit-mask-composite: xor;
        mask-composite: exclude;
        opacity: 0;
        transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }

    .pillar-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-8px);
        box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(211, 197, 136, 0.15);
    }

    .pillar-card:hover::before {
        opacity: 1;
    }

    .pillar-icon {
        width: 80px;
        height: 80px;
        margin: 0 auto 30px;
        color: #d3c588;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .pillar-icon svg {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .pillar-title {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #fff;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-family:
            system-ui,
            -apple-system,
            sans-serif;
    }

    .pillar-description {
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 300;
        color: #e0e0e0;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin: 0;
        font-family:
            system-ui,
            -apple-system,
            sans-serif;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .methodology-pillars {
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .pillars-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .pillar-card {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .pillar-icon {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .pillar-title {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .pillar-description {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
    }
</style>
